          "date": "2014-04-09 07:36:08.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-4593 ptlrpc: req could loop forever in sending list",
        "message": "LU-4593 ptlrpc: req could loop forever in sending list\n\nIn ptlrpc_check_set(), when a request runs into\nRQ_PHASE_UNREGISTERING phase, if the reply is successfully unlinked,\nthe unregistered flag should be set accordingly, otherwise the\nrequest could possibly run into interpret section and repeat the reply\nunregister.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam.xu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I3e272bdeace5610a094ca4579f41794c4bf41031\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_4"
    }
